## Key constraints
- Vanilla JS only -- no TypeScript, no Node.js APIs, no npm packages in app/
- LAI database (LAI_categorised.csv) is core IP -- never send to external APIs
- Touch it, extract it -- any index.html section opened must be extracted to app/js/ in the same PR
- Third-party libs live in app/js/lib/ -- never edit these files (OrbitControls.js, three.module.js)
- Icons always inline SVG, never <img> with PNG
- Two coordinate systems must stay strictly separate: Global (Three.js world, -Z = True North) and Design (user-set via designNorthAngle)
- Always propose + get approval before writing any file
- scene units = metres; world north = -Z axis; Y axis = up

